1.title: Guys, Gals and Gabe
1.plot: Host Greg Fitzsimmons ambushes unsuspecting customers at gas stations around the country and challenges them to win cash on Pumped! This week from East Meadow, New York, Bensalem, Pennsylvania, and Jefferson Valley, New York.

imdb.plot outline: Pumped! is a fast-paced, ambush-style quiz show that transforms everyday people into instant game show contestants, all while filling up their gas tanks at their local service station. Host Greg Fitzsimmons guides players through multiple rounds of automotive and pop culture question and answer games, affording them the opportunity to win cash and prizes while fueling their cars.
